Depends: R (>= 3.0)
Imports: gtools, gdata, stats, caTools, KernSmooth
Suggests: grid, MASS
Description: Various R programming tools for plotting data, including: local
  smoothing, enhanced versions of standard plots, manipulating colors,
  two-dimensional data summaries, enhanced regression diagnostic plots, formula
  interface to lowess, text plots, balloon plots, Venn diagrams, Open-Office style
  plots, separate y axes, means and confidence intervals, and a spaced scatter
  plot where points do not overlap.
